title: Closing stock prices for Akef Inc. on Wednesday
summary: This chart shows the Closing Stock Price for Akef Inc. from Monday to Friday .
It reached approximately £ 51.4 on Monday , rising to £ 62.0 on Tuesday , reaching a peak of £ 74.38 on Wednesday , before falling to around £ 21.9 on Thursday and just under £ 10 on Friday .
